content.description: Start at the right side on two slopey points. Cross over with your right and continue on out the hole in the roof :D
content.protection: A spotter and a couple pads would've been nice but I sent it without so just keep ur eyes on the road and hands upon the wheel.
content.location: Up the hill from the Vegan roughly 70-80 yards. Can't miss it. The Store Boulder and Winter's Warmth are within 20 yards of the cave's entrance

content.description: Little dangerous with not the best rock quality, Most of the time is filled with garbage.  If you are to boulder here bring plenty of pads on spotter. A fall from above would not be ideal.
